29,"Before our bottles head into the filling room, they’re carefully checked for visual perfection. Here, an approved batch waits to be hand-filled. We fill only 100 – 200 bottles of each product at a time, so that products are as fresh as possible when they’re shipped out. None of our products sit on the shelf for more than two weeks before they are sent to a customer."
